OOC: Sorry I haven't been posting, but i was at a friends and i was sick all 
last week. :-P

* SHadow Cat ignores the she-wolf and looks at the cuddly ball of fuzz in 
her arms, it's large, green eyes gaze back at her and she mewed pitiously. 
Shadow Cat smiled and looked at Snow Tech,*

" I think we have a new friend!"

* Snow Tech sighs and walks over, looking at the black kitten.*

" I think it's a mutant dust bunny. It looks like one anyway."

* He pokes the kittens fur and was rewarded with a small, but painful, bite 
on the end of his finger.*

" Yeowtch! That thing has teeth!"

*Shadow Cat laughs and walks towards the woods, motioning with her head for 
Snow Tech to follow. He grunts through his frowning face and follows, 
sucking on the injured finger. They stop in a small clearing and look 
around, it looked peacful and seren. But they knew appearances could be 
deceptive. Without letting their gaurd down, they headed into they clearing, 
probing with their minds to see if anyone, or thing, was their. Nothing was. 
Just an owl and a few small mice. Shadow Cat looks at Snow tech*

" I think it's one of 'em, but we'd have to probe to make sure, are you 
able?"

*SNow Tech grins and nods,*

" You bet your skip-plate i am!"

* SHe sighs and hands him the kitten,*

" Then lets begin........"
